pageContext.claim: “Think of it, I have a one-on-one meeting with Putin like I do with every other leader. I have many one-on-one -- nobody ever says anything about it. But with Putin they say, oh, what did they talk about? We talked about very positive things because -- look, we are beating everybody.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump's meeting with Putin was not like his meetings with "every other leader." It's highly unusual for a president to meet with a foreign leader without any staff present.
